{"tid":2366236,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普敦促 : 不要出現暴力、違法和任何形式的破壞行為。這不是他和美國所主張的 !","createTime":"2021-01-14T10:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T11:17:11.000Z","uid":219007,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf41bc20217fe1228e4384ce6075d48e5933899","tid":2366236,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"在美國國會眾議院通過彈劾後，總統特朗普發表錄影講話，未有回應彈劾，而是繼續譴責上星期衝擊國會事件，又呼籲支持者保持和平。<br />\n<br />\n長約五分鐘的講話，是透過美國政府的官方Twitter發表，特朗普重申他的真正支持者不會容忍暴力，任何人參與上星期的暴力，應受到司法制裁。他要求支持者尋求方法，紓緩緊張局勢，認為每個美國人的聲音都應該以和平的方式被聆聽。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普強調，已經指示聯邦機構，動用所需資源，確保權力過渡有序進行，重申必須以國家利益為首要考慮。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，特朗普發表聲明，稱鑑於更多關於示威活動的報道，他敦促不要出現暴力、違法和任何形式的破壞行為。這不是他和美國所主張的。特朗普呼籲所有美國人協助緩和緊張局勢，平息怒火。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570307-20210114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570307-20210114.htm&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVYMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=4f38b341\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570307-20210114.htm&h=11b8e7e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570307-20210114.htm</a>"},{"pid":"caf15709569d5d1565bfd31ce27e6388db9eca52","tid":2366236,"uid":238369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"左膠：唔係真心，講反話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59f995656a60c4f61761dc5fea9d83420865848","tid":2366236,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:26:43.000Z","msg":"啲民兵聽到佢咁講應該心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897afcbac71a4f0a4fc0274c4a1635a78c2626bb","tid":23662